Package: PRIMR
Type: Package
Title: Remove gDNA contamination and mispriming reads from Targeted scRNA-seq  
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Theo", "Botella", , "tbotella@nygenome.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0331-2491"))
Maintainer: Theo Botella <tbotella@nygenome.org>
Description: PRIMR has been develop in the context of amplicons targeted concurrent scRNA+DNA sequencing. It allows for filtering of mRNA reads mapping to intronic regions (indicative of potential gDNA) and/or ambiguous reads lacking the anticipated exon-exon junction.
